side-effects:
Side-effects nausea, vomiting, abdominal pain; chest pain,
arrhythmias (including bradycardia), palpitation, hypertension, vasoconstriction;
dyspnoea, pulmonary oedema; headache, dizziness; tinnitus; rash; very rarely myocardial infarction

